      <title>安联经济学家苏布兰谈美联储、欧洲央行降息和油价影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/a-10-rise-in-oil-would-raise-european-inflation-by-1-2-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安联首席经济学家 Ludovic Subran 预计欧洲央行今年将降息 50 个基点 - 然而，石油价格上涨可能会使央行的情况变得复杂，并削弱对美联储降息的预期。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/a-10-rise-in-oil-would-raise-european-inflation-by-1-2-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 10:09:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易员正在为 5% 的收益率、不降息的世界做准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/bond-traders-shift-thinking-to-a-5-yield-no-rate-cut-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储今年不降息的可能性越来越大，债券交易员正在为 10 年期美国国债收益率突破 5% 做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/bond-traders-shift-thinking-to-a-5-yield-no-rate-cut-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 07:40:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
